  "text": "Thank you. During this first 25, 000-year cycle was there any industrial development at all, was there any machinery available during this period to the people? I am Ra. Using the term \"machine\" to the meaning which you ascribe, the answer is no. However, there were, shall we say, various implements of wood and rock which were used in order to obtain food and for use in aggression.",
